00052 void FusionCHPMultiDataDataTest::testRead()
00053 {
00054         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::Read("../../parsers/data/CHP_MultiData_file");
00055         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chp != NULL);
00056         FusionCHPMultiDataData *genoChp = FusionCHPMultiDataData::FromBase(chp); 
00057         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp != NULL);
00058 
00059 
00060     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataExpressionData ex;
00061     affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetMultiDataGenotypeData gn;
00062         ParameterNameValueType param;
00063 
00064         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetAlgName() == L"sig");
00065         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetAlgVersion() == L"1.0");
00066         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetArrayType() == L"test3");
00067         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 1);
00068         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00069         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(ExpressionControlMultiDataType) == 3);
00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetEntryCount(GenotypeControlMultiDataType) == 1);
00071 
00072     // expression
00073     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionMultiDataType) == 0);
00074     genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00075         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 10.0f, 0.0001f);
00076         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ex1");
00077 
00078     // genotype
00079     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeMultiDataType) == 2);
00080     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0) == L"int");
00081     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetMetricColumnName(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1) == L"float");
00082 
00083     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 1);
00085         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 11.0f, 0.0001f);
00086         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn1");
00087     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00088     param = gn.metrics[0];
00089     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00090     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 1);
00091     param = gn.metrics[1];
00092     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00093     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 2.0f, 0.00001f);
00094 
00095     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeMultiDataType, 1, gn);
00096         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00097         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00098         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gn2");
00099     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 2);
00100     param = gn.metrics[0];
00101     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::Int32Type);
00102     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueInt32() == 2);
00103     param = gn.metrics[1];
00104     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetParameterType() == ParameterNameValueType::FloatType);
00105     CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(param.GetValueFloat(), 3.0f, 0.00001f);
00106 
00107 
00108     // genotype control
00109     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(GenotypeControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00110     genoChp->GetGenotypeEntry(GenotypeControlMultiDataType, 0, gn);
00111         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.call == 2);
00112         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(gn.confidence, 22.0f, 0.0001f);
00113         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.metrics.size() == 0);
00114         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(gn.name == "gc1");
00115 
00116 
00117 
00118     // expression control
00119     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(genoChp->GetNumMetricColumns(ExpressionControlMultiDataType) == 0);
00120         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 0, ex);
00121         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 20.0f, 0.0001f);
00122         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec1");
00123         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 1, ex);
00124         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 30.0f, 0.0001f);
00125         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec2");
00126         genoChp->GetExpressionEntry(ExpressionControlMultiDataType, 2, ex);
00127         CPPUNIT_ASSERT_DOUBLES_EQUAL(ex.quantification, 40.0f, 0.0001f);
00128         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(ex.name == "ec3");
00129 
00130         delete genoChp;

00163 
00164     cnChp->GetCopyNumberEntry(CopyNumberMultiDataType, 0, e);
00165         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.chr == 10);

00167         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
